    "Reason : 1 - The proposed development would fail to provide adequate internal and external space, resulting in substandard living conditions for future occupiers of the development. The proposal is therefore contrary to London Plan policy D6 (Housing quality and standards) and Local Plan policy SC5 (Ensuring suitable internal and external space).  \r\n",
    "Reason : 2 - The submission fails to demonstrate that the proposed development would maximise the opportunities for carbon reduction on site at each stage of the energy hierarchy. The proposal is therefore contrary to London Plan policies SI2 (Minimising greenhouse gas emissions), SI3 (Energy infrastructure) and SI4 (Managing heat risk) and Local Plan policies EQ1 (Energy and carbon reduction) and EQ2 (Sustainable design and construction).\r\n"
